    <item>
      <title>pet questions</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=magiciantactics&amp;message.id=400#M400</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;I recently made an alt mage.&amp;nbsp; I've been looking for information on the pets, but have had little success.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;What I have learned from personal experience is the following:&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Fire pet cast a self DS, and kills pretty fast.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Earth pet roots, and seems to have decent survivability&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Water pet seems to proc or cast something, but not sure what&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
